"""Build a source-aware register of Austrian public web presences.

Live sources:
- oesterreich.gv.at municipality picker and authority directory
- Schulen-Online national school directory

Output deliberately separates organizations from websites. Missing homepages remain
visible as missing; no domain is guessed.
"""
